Xegony is FFA on most spawns till just recently. And even then there is only a handfull of guilds in the Rotation / Council of guilds.<br>
There was this guild called Cognatus comprised of exactly 9 players who hand no less then 4 PC's each. This Guild was built of well to do family and friends who enjoyed monopolizing as many large mob kills in Kunark. They were constanly in contact with each other had the spawns down to a T. There wasnt a spawn on VS that wasnt theirs for months strait. They quickly grew in wealth but lacked one thing Emarr has in its diversity. That is size. <br>
 Other guilds realized the strength of Cognatus and started complaining. Not understanding why a guild of so few could do so well and move with such precision. The council of guilds on Xegony was formed after a group of guilds used Cognatus'  only weakness against them and shut them out of everything Cognatus had previously shut them out of. <br>
  My point is here we have grown as a server to work together in this rotation. Stoping it now will hurt Emarr alot more and shut down what we are so well known for and that is our diversity. Going FFA would make the weaker weak the mediocre weak and the strogest remain strong. Without the numbers Magister MF RoD CE Affliction UI and DG have guilds like MC PC RoN and the like will regress due to lack of player cooperation. <br>
<br>
